@DATABASE "After The War Part 2"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - A - After The War Part 2"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - A
                   ====================================

                           After The War Part 2
                           ====================


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====
            
@{"Infinite Lives " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(49001,0)"}         49001,0
@{"Infinite Time  " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(49202,0)"}         49202,0
@{"Infinite Energy" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(56056,0)"}         56056,0
@{"Infinite Ammo  " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(50020,0)"}         50020,0
@{"Immunity       " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(49820,201)"}         49820,201
@{"Lives = x      " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(48831,255)"}         48831,x (x= 1-255)

                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).

                         And in case you're wondering, there is a
                         difference between "Infinite Energy" and
                         "Immunity". With the "Immunity" POKE, your
                         energy bar goes down, but nothing kills
                         you, whereas with "Infinite Energy", your
                         bar stays still, but you can be killed by
                         the falling bombs.

                         Ok, so I could have just put the two
                         together as one POKE, but I thought it
                         was better to give you a choice!

                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
